<article class="page-content">
  <header class="page-header">
    <p class="eyebrow">Learning tracks</p>
    <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  </header>

  <section class="columns-board">
    <div class="columns-intro">
      <span>Learning tracks</span>
      <p>把零散笔记整理成可以连续阅读的路线。每个专栏都围绕一个长期主题展开，适合按顺序慢慢补齐。</p>
    </div>

    <a class="column-track is-active-track" href="<%- url_for('/engineering/') %>">
      <span class="column-index">01</span>
      <div>
        <span class="column-kicker">正在更新</span>
        <h2>前端工程化</h2>
        <p>模块化、构建工具、包管理、Monorepo、代码规范和 CI/CD。关注一个前端项目如何长期稳定地开发和发布。</p>
      </div>
    </a>

    <div class="columns-queue">
      <article class="column-track">
        <span class="column-index">02</span>
        <div>
          <span class="column-kicker">准备中</span>
          <h2>CSS 布局</h2>
          <p>Flex、Grid、响应式、对齐、间距和日常页面排版。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="column-track">
        <span class="column-index">03</span>
        <div>
          <span class="column-kicker">准备中</span>
          <h2>JavaScript 核心机制</h2>
          <p>作用域、原型链、事件循环、异步模型和浏览器运行机制。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="column-track">
        <span class="column-index">04</span>
        <div>
          <span class="column-kicker">稍后</span>
          <h2>React / Next.js</h2>
          <p>组件设计、渲染模式、路由、数据获取和工程实践。</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="column-track">
        <span class="column-index">05</span>
        <div>
          <span class="column-kicker">稍后</span>
          <h2>DevOps 与部署</h2>
          <p>Git 规范、Nginx、自动化发布和 Web 服务部署基础。</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</article>
